{"tid":142644,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今日有隻90後問我拎OT補水 俾我屌到喊","createTime":"2017-03-04T03:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T11:53:54.000Z","uid":68867,"like":1,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b70857cb548b3fdc0dc27b1f89a02231dd2f1c29","tid":142644,"uid":68867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:14:38.000Z","msg":"話說今日有隻90後門都冇kock就咁走入黎<br />\n我見佢好似有急事咁 就大人有大量冇屌獲佢<br />\n點知隻90後咁撚樣講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  90後 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「老細，我尋日OT左成晚 冇訓過 想問老細你OT個到點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n我即刻無名火起 一下拍落張枱到屌佢一獲勁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「補？我補你老母啊！係咪OT個幾粒鐘都要同公司計？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住隻90後想喊想喊咁同我講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「我...我OT左...成個星期...每日都OT到3，4點。為左份PJ...都只係想拎番份消夜錢姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ...」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「你都算好野la wo，公司都冇同你計到咁足，你同公司計到咁足？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  公司有冇同你計水電煤？有冇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  公司俾個地方你做野 有冇收你錢？有冇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  即刻同我死返出去做野，做唔曬唔好諗住走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n跟住佢就死死咁出返去<br />\n見佢咁慘臨走前叫左佢一下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「喂，你隻90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n佢滿心期待<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「係 老細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「聽日記得準時時返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」"},{"pid":"67bb1512f9001920a8b8352918aa12f4cde5167e","tid":142644,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:16:26.000Z","msg":"做得好呀Ching"},{"pid":"40b29a0a037a039c13e79bf9cb79f44975503a24","tid":142644,"uid":36702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:20:48.000Z","msg":"真係辛苦你打一大篇廢話<br />\n<br />\n等我留個名支持下你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8087cb267de99b2d0e1aadbd4f666f1e8ae23f","tid":142644,"uid":61106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T18:47:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係辛苦你打一大篇廢話<br />\n<br />\n等我留個名支持下你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab057506093f3846f8f1c12c1fa4e555c96768fd","tid":142644,"uid":17524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T10:15:27.000Z","msg":"多d同吉魯ching學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6aeb4ea9554b6899c6bddfc6c798dc34e57d4d","tid":142644,"uid":36029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T10:24:30.000Z","msg":"玩唔厭架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088c491699b853cb7dc3aaacceffb519862793b2","tid":142644,"uid":87971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T10:27:54.000Z","msg":"老細 你knock都唔識串<br />\n利申 90後"},{"pid":"62042127235cd5454afa0a52f5623398c94dea80","tid":142644,"uid":5